     <h1>Welcome to the Administration and Planning Division </h1> 
     <h5><strong>A message from Vice President Chris Call </strong></h5> 
     <p><img src="images/Chris08.jpg" width="80" height="80" alt="Chris"></p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="../president/exec_team.html#Call">Chris Call</a> </p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space">805.565.6023</p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="mailto:ccall@westmont.edu">ccall@westmont.edu</a></p> 
     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
     <p class="txt_blockquote">The Administration and Planning Division provides multiple services in support of the college's programs and operations. The division is comprised of:</p> 
     <table width="432" border="1" bordercolor="#FFFFFF"> 
      <tbody>
       <tr valign="top"> 
        <td width="236" align="center" valign="top"><p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="../auxiliary_services/"><strong>Auxiliary Services</strong></a></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">ATM Machine</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">College Store</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Dining Services</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Post Office</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Reprographics</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><strong><a href="../../conferences/"><strong><strong></strong></strong></a><strong><strong><a href="../college_counsel/">College Counsel </a></strong></strong></strong></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="../human_resources/"><strong>Human Resources</strong></a></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Benefits</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Employee Handbook</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Holiday Schedule</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Resources for New Hires</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> </td> 
        <td width="180" align="center" valign="top"><p class="txt_indent_no_space"><strong><a href="../procurement/">Procurement</a></strong></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><strong><strong>Public Events </strong></strong></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="documents/PublicEvents.pdf">Overview - available items</a></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><a href="documents/PlanninganEventatWestmont.pdf">Accomplishing your goal</a> </p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><strong><a href="../risk/index.html">Risk Management</a></strong></p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> <p class="txt_indent_no_space"><strong><a href="../planning/index.html">Strategic Planning</a></strong></p> </td> 
       </tr> 
      </tbody>
     </table> 
     <p class="txt_blockquote">I trust that the information provided on this page will give you quick access to the leaders in these areas, and to services provided through the division and college. If you can't find what you need, please contact me or a member of my staff."</p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Blessings,</p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space">Chris Call </p> 
     <p class="txt_indent_no_space">&nbsp;</p> 
